manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Multipurpose cooking in a compact countertop design The Total Chef 4-Slice Toaster Oven offers multipurpose cooking in a compact countertop design, perfect for small kitchens, apartments, and dorm rooms. Toast bread, bake biscuits, grill chicken wings, and more in this 1000 watt unit with easy-to-use timer and temperature control knobs. This unit comes with an aluminized baking pan, chrome wire rack, and crumb tray that are removable for easy cleanup. This convenient toaster oven features a wide temperature range of 200-450°F (93-232°C) to suit all your cooking needs. The 30-minute timer with automatic shut-off allows for precise and controlled toasting; or use the Stay On function for longer cooking times. The upper and lower heating elements cycle on and off during the cooking process to maintain a consistent temperature throughout. This simple little appliance will quickly become one of your favorites!

TCTO09 Total Chef 4-Slice Toaster Oven ENERGY-EFFICIENT Use this small but powerful 1000W toaster oven to cook meals for one or two or whip up a quick snack without wasting energy or heating up the whole kitchen SPACE-SAVING DESIGN This compact 4-slice toaster oven with a 14.6 x 12.75 inch footprint fits easily on a shelf or under a cupboard, making it ideal for small kitchens, RVs, and dorm rooms USER-FRIENDLY CONTROLS Simple dial controls take the guesswork out of setting the oven temperature from 200-450°F (93-232°C), selecting the "Stay On" function, or setting the timer for up to 30 minutes

TCTO09 Total Chef 4-Slice Toaster Oven SAFETY FEATURES Built-in safety features include an LED power indicator, timer cooking with automatic shut off, non-slip feet, cool-touch door handle, and wall spacers to ensure room space for venting HASSLE-FREE CLEANUP Your Total Chef toaster oven comes with an aluminized baking pan, chrome wire rack, and removable crumb tray that are dishwasher safe for easy cleanup MODERN BLACK AND SILVER With its sleek black finish, this 4 slice toaster oven suits any decor and matches perfectly with the suite of elegant small appliances from Total Chef

Multipurpose cooking in a compact countertop design, perfect for small kitchens, apartments, and dorm rooms! Toast bread, bake biscuits, grill chicken wings, and more without heating up your whole kitchen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The little toaster that could!
reviews.reviewText: It's a very small toaster oven, but it's perfect for my small apartment that doesn't have a lot of counter space. I was looking at microwaves, but they're all insanely priced nowadays. I saw toaster ovens seemed to be way cheaper and found this one. I like the idea that I'm reheating something and not microwaving it too. The quality of food is better tasting in my opinion. It's been great for toast, reheating leftovers, and much more. A little tray is included, and a tip to keep your tray clean is to cover it with aluminum foil. You can change it out when it gets a little icky and your tray is still in perfect condition!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We got this after our oven quit. Just until we can get a full stove and oven. But can't even fit an 8×8 cake pan. It says it fits for pieces of toast, yeah cause there's no room for anything else you can just barely fit that. If u are a 1 person house go for it but if you have this as a 2ed over don't waste your time.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This toaster oven is utter garbage The pictures are misleading. This reminds me of Swiss Colony's creative photography. The material it's made of is most certainly not steel. It's more like tin. As far as capacity. There is no way this gadget will hold what it's advertised to hold. You'd be lucky to squeeze a single chicken leg in it. Absolute garbage. Overpriced as well. The delivery was delayed as well. There are much better options on the market. I suggest you explore and compare. My first thought was to throw the piece of junk in the garbage dumpster when I first opened it. If I didn't pay such an outrageous price for it I most certainly would have. But the piece of is being returned. Hopefully I'll get a refund.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This little oven is just perfect for when you don't want to use the big oven to heat 1 piece. It's also handy when you want your food to remain crispy during reheat, versus soft microwave results. It's a bit smaller than I expected, but it has proved itself a value.

reviews.reviewText: It arrived but came without any tray, rack or other extra parts. It won't be of any use this way and I can't get to a post office so guess I am just out on this one. Will review my rating if I ever get the parts to make this wee thing work, right now I am quite angry. The warehouse was at fault, they shipped only the toaster in a box that said air fryer. Got a second one today and IT WORKS, is in the proper box and has all the extra parts. So I gave it a 5 star.
